<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Athletics' Olivares on DL  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   KANSAS CITY, Mo. (AP) -- A day after leaving his start against
Kansas City after just one batter, Oakland right-hander Omar
Olivares was placed on the 15-day disabled list Saturday.
</P>
<P>
   Olivares, (3-8, 6.64 ERA) strained a muscle in his pitching
shoulder.
</P>
<P>
   Right-handed reliever Luis Vizcaino was recalled from Triple-A
Sacramento to take his spot on the roster.
</P>
<P>
   Vizcaino was 1-1 with a 7.20 ERA in Sacramento. This will be his
third stint with the A's this year. He is 0-1 with a 6.87 ERA in 10
relief appearances with the A's.
</P>
</TEXT>
