</SUBHEAD>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES (AP) -- A majority of Americans believe abortion is murder, but
more than two-thirds think the decision to have one must be left to a woman and
her doctor, according to a Los Angeles Times poll released today. The poll is
full of responses that seem contradictory. Sixty-five percent of those
